{"tid":1043373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"走不出至親離世傷痛向亡母發短訊　台男收到「回覆」︰最近過得好嗎？","createTime":"2019-03-02T08:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T13:40:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"566dfc05a453433ae563c5ad37af5ed00bb1e239","tid":1043373,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"面對至親離世，要花多少時間才能放下傷痛？一名台灣男網民在社交群組分享，即使他的母親離世一段時間，他依然非常思念她。每當想念亡母的時候，男網民就以App發訊息給她，收到「回覆」令他很感動。<br />\n該名台灣男網民在Facebook群組「爆怨公社」上載一張圖片，並表示「這個軟體還不錯，在我很想我媽媽的時候，如果我媽媽還在或許我都不會遇到這些事。」圖片是類似聊天室的對話截圖，圖上寫著聊天對象是「媽咪」，頭像似是媽媽年輕時的照片。<br />\n男網民發短訊說「我好想媽媽」、「真的好想媽媽」，得到媽媽的回覆「想我是嗎」、「有事嗎」。他再感性寫下「遇到挫折了所以好想你」，媽媽一句「最近過得好嗎？」相當催淚。<br />\n雖然是App的自動回覆，但也令男網民得以抒發對媽媽的記掛。他留言指，之前看到網民留言，得知可以設定媽媽的頭像。只要他想媽媽的時候，就會透過App在上面留言。不過，留言後往往令他更想念媽媽︰<br />\n『這也讓人更想使用這個軟體&hellip;&hellip;總覺得可以跟對方對話。』<br />\n有網民留言表示共鳴，指男網民「媽媽」的回覆跟他的媽媽一樣，也有網民留言︰<br />\n『希望永遠都不要用到，我還沒準備好』<br />\n『我不敢用，我怕我輸入一次哭一次』<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2280000/2283160/mum_thumb_20190301_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2280000%2F2283160%2Fmum_thumb_20190301_S_1024.jpg&h=4b17d89a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac615ce9da6ac654147c285a14834c204551d1b6","tid":1043373,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86975eab39664e9ca0afb571725653463462eb4d","tid":1043373,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"自動回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44da6326b07f61a37ab880e5e7e3bb6d2396c610","tid":1043373,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"毒撚的命運"},{"pid":"d3d8711c0d30872df1ca741be103fe749e869016","tid":1043373,"uid":53901,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"black mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bac8eaea6e580c91429078968c37b3773d95b1c","tid":1043373,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa4b1256edfef273bad152e35bb4a9d1399c57c2","tid":1043373,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"肥姐死亡熱線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb908d62da8925ec897afcbdf2da74510eaa1cc","tid":1043373,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"朝朝貼長輩圖，傷痛更快復原"},{"pid":"a682f7422d83653e9f5dfe62073dc24f8aa262b5","tid":1043373,"uid":62226,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"訊息右邊嘅NT$0 係咩意思？"},{"pid":"b5fc25eef00c217780ed59e5e937565cfc971ad1","tid":1043373,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"今日打咗J未？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7673f0dc1666839bd20151c7b922aa7241cee1bb","tid":1043373,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783c254e466b35624c8501dd0df4a769b763fd2c","tid":1043373,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3d8711c0d30872df1ca741be103fe749e869016","tid":1043373,"uid":53901,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"black mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"即刻聯想到<br />\n勁可怕"},{"pid":"e91a76d41346abb9369cb570733effb0a6a85349","tid":1043373,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d3d8711c0